title: Global revenue of Birkenstock 2012 to 2013
summary: The chart at hand is a line chart where the x axis denotes Year and a y axis denotes Revenue in million euros. In total the number of data points it has is 2.
Overall Revenue in million euros has increased over the Year.
Revenue in million euros is slightly increasing from 2012 to 2013.
The steepest increase occurs in between the Year 2012 and 2013.
Maximum Revenue in million euros, about 14525.69 was reported at Year 2013
The lowest Revenue in million euros, of value 14109.4 was reported at Year 2012
